d-company.png 933w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-company-300x208.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-company-768x533.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-company-60x42.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-company-150x104.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 933px) 100vw, 933px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>You can also change order of the field \u2013 This is used if you have multiple fields for the same feature and you want to re-oder how they will be shown to the customer.<\/p>\n<p>After filling up the new custom field\u00a0<strong>click Save.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>When <strong>new custom field for company\u00a0is created<\/strong> you need to navigate\u00a0to<strong> Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;Company<\/strong>\u00a0to give this field value.<\/p>\n<p>Give this new\u00a0custom field values here eq. Street Name 553.<br \/>\nClick <strong>Save Settings.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-large wp-image-294 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-edit-1024x472-1024x472.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"980\" height=\"452\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-edit-1024x472.png 1024w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-edit-1024x472-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-edit-1024x472-768x354.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-edit-1024x472-60x28.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/custom-field-edit-1024x472-150x69.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/custom-fields\/\"><strong>Read more<\/strong><\/a> about custom fields<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<